{"tid":1829533,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"習近平被翻譯作「糞坑先生」Facebook道歉","createTime":"2020-01-18T20:59:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-18T22:02:59.000Z","uid":125168,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"be1a03870513f6a75953028d04a8913d41a8d86b","tid":1829533,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T20:59:23.000Z","msg":"Facebook為習近平名字不雅翻譯致歉<br />\n<br />\n社交網站Facebook為國家主席習近平國事訪問緬甸期間，名字的英文翻譯出錯成為不雅用字道歉。習近平在第二天訪問期間，在首都內比都與緬甸國務資政昂山素姬會面，並簽署多項貿易協議。昂山素姬在她官方Facebook專頁發布聲明提到習近平抵達時，內容由緬甸語自動翻譯成英語時，習近平被稱作「糞坑先生」，而且不只出現一次。Facebook發言人事後說，已解決了翻譯問題，並確保問題不再發生，並為由此引起的冒犯，真誠地道歉。<span style=\"color: gold;\">Facebook沒有交代事件是由黑客入侵、軟件或其他問題引起。</span><br />\n<br />\n2020-01-19 04:54:19"},{"pid":"bb4edb1faba671d5b35ac07e2e3ac0fcf261aec0","tid":1829533,"uid":201604,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T21:00:37.000Z","msg":"屎賤平"},{"pid":"b163715f849a21e3c0712634f6ee41694e93e25d","tid":1829533,"uid":125168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T21:00:51.000Z","msg":"Facebook前線好黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f6d99853fd63c7cb5549723c779d47458e69018","tid":1829533,"uid":125168,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bb4edb1faba671d5b35ac07e2e3ac0fcf261aec0","tid":1829533,"uid":201604,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T21:00:37.000Z","msg":"屎賤平"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T21:01:14.000Z","msg":"咁諗落又無譯錯"},{"pid":"9ca9eb296f55944ddc148f332423d850b10ea51e","tid":1829533,"uid":42283,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T21:07:57.000Z","msg":"人地AI指出真相姐"},{"pid":"2d3406443cf96f4e30a595892c471a77ae7d9f2f","tid":1829533,"uid":9640,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T21:11:20.000Z","msg":"糞坑先生<br />\n藝名咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d498c7df82b18f9cb2903757e21cb4ee8dd1bb66","tid":1829533,"uid":2